1
00:00:05,930 --> 00:00:08,609
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,609 --> 00:00:12,064
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,064 --> 00:00:18,257
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,257 --> 00:00:24,383
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,383 --> 00:00:31,004
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:31,004 --> 00:00:35,990
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:35,990 --> 00:00:43,290
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:48,314
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,314 --> 00:00:49,827
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,827 --> 00:00:55,690
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,690 --> 00:01:00,590
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:00,590 --> 00:01:08,457
♫  With your reflection being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,457 --> 00:01:11,781
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:20,812
Gao Yang, actually today, Mr. Gao has been trying to tell you...

15
00:01:20,812 --> 00:01:22,865
I know.

16
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:27,419
He wants to say he hates to part with me and he wants me to stay.

17
00:01:27,419 --> 00:01:28,660
You know?

18
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:32,959
I watched him grow up. How can I not know?

19
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:39,219
Since you know he hates to part with you, why won't you have a nice chat with him?

20
00:01:39,219 --> 00:01:40,859
What should we talk about?

21
00:01:40,859 --> 00:01:45,040
We would argue every time we talk. After that, he would get angry.

22
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:47,180
Once he gets angry, he would hit me.

23
00:01:47,180 --> 00:01:51,144
Talking to him... wouldn't that be asking for a beating?

24
00:01:51,144 --> 00:01:53,700
But I don't think Mr. Gao is someone like that.

25
00:01:53,700 --> 00:01:54,979
He...

26
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,419
I know him better than anyone.

27
00:01:57,419 --> 00:02:00,360
He'll be like that for the rest of his life.

28
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:03,500
After he was injured in the National University Games, his life was all downhill from there.

29
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:06,620
He wasn't qualified for an academic title and he gave up on the soccer team halfway through.

30
00:02:06,620 --> 00:02:08,799
Tell me, what else can he do?

31
00:02:10,659 --> 00:02:14,819
In my opinion, he's very persistent.

32
00:02:14,819 --> 00:02:16,379
Persistent?

33
00:02:16,379 --> 00:02:19,220
Yeah, right. Let's hurry and go to sleep.

34
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:45,380
When Mr. Gao first came to the orphanage to find me,

35
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:48,299
I never thought about leaving.

36
00:02:48,299 --> 00:02:51,499
He kept contacting me that year

37
00:02:52,580 --> 00:02:55,519
and kept convincing me to go to Tieyuan's No.3 High School.

38
00:02:55,519 --> 00:02:57,669
I never agreed to it,

39
00:03:00,980 --> 00:03:06,160
but later on, I found out he was also doing something else.

40
00:03:12,559 --> 00:03:14,590
What was it?

41
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:17,580
Xiaowen, please just come to Tieyuan with me.

42
00:03:17,580 --> 00:03:21,080
I really am your parents' friend. Let me help you!

43
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,539
Thank you. You really don't have to.

44
00:03:27,539 --> 00:03:29,539
I found Mi Jia's family.

45
00:03:30,460 --> 00:03:33,779
I found Mi Jia's aunt.

46
00:03:33,779 --> 00:03:37,940
You don't want to go to Tieyuan because you're worried about Mi Jia, right?

47
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:40,260
You can both come together now.

48
00:03:40,260 --> 00:03:41,939
Is that okay?

49
00:03:41,939 --> 00:03:45,280
That... Wasn't it the police who found her aunt?

50
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:48,079
The police did indeed help him contact her.

51
00:03:48,079 --> 00:03:51,939
But it was Mr. Gao who initiated the search.

52
00:03:51,939 --> 00:03:54,360
He posted missing person notices everywhere including

53
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:59,200
radio stations, newspapers, and bus stations.

54
00:03:59,200 --> 00:04:01,881
I heard he also borrowed money from everyone in the end.

55
00:04:02,680 --> 00:04:04,389
Look at this.

56
00:04:05,430 --> 00:04:08,030
[2004 National Track and Field Competition for High Schools Registration Form]

57
00:04:08,679 --> 00:04:12,460
The National Track and Field Competition for High Schools?

58
00:04:12,460 --> 00:04:15,420
If you can rank within the top three, your tuition will be waived.

59
00:04:15,420 --> 00:04:18,639
If you come to Tieyuan, you can participate in this competition.

60
00:04:20,219 --> 00:04:23,360
The dean told me you've always wanted to

61
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:25,360
go to you parents' Alma mater, the Beijing University of Technology.

62
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:28,500
But you wouldn't dare to apply because the tuition is too expensive.

63
00:04:28,500 --> 00:04:32,519
If you participate in this competition, you will have a chance.

64
00:04:33,539 --> 00:04:37,340
That's why the two of us decided to come to Tieyuan's No. 3 High School.

65
00:04:43,299 --> 00:04:44,984
Xiaowen,

66
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:50,140
the things you just told me... which year did it happen?

67
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:53,180
Last year.

68
00:04:53,180 --> 00:04:54,910
- Last year?
- Yes.

69
00:05:01,099 --> 00:05:06,736
No wonder Gao Bin suddenly gave up on the soccer team

70
00:05:06,736 --> 00:05:09,280
and Dong Dawei started to make trouble for me.

71
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:11,280
Dong Dawei...

72
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:13,133
Last year...

73
00:05:14,820 --> 00:05:17,299
It's... It's because of me?

74
00:05:20,439 --> 00:05:22,424
I'm sorry.

75
00:05:23,659 --> 00:05:25,434
It's okay.

76
00:05:31,922 --> 00:05:38,723
[Episode 9: I Just Didn't Know How To Tell Him]

77
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:11,260
- How about we listen to some songs for a bit?
- We'll do that later.

78
00:06:13,520 --> 00:06:15,806
I have a few words to say.

79
00:06:15,806 --> 00:06:18,917
- Gao Yang...
- I know

80
00:06:18,917 --> 00:06:21,200
you're reluctant to part with me.

81
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:26,800
As for me, I'm actually quite reluctant to leave home, too.

82
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,576
Just a little.

83
00:06:28,576 --> 00:06:31,652
- You're not leaving anymore?
- I'm still leaving.

84
00:06:31,652 --> 00:06:35,059
But I can come back during breaks.

85
00:06:35,059 --> 00:06:37,219
Gao Yang, I'll let you go.

86
00:06:37,979 --> 00:06:40,068
I've thought it through.

87
00:06:40,068 --> 00:06:42,835
It's better if you go to Beijing.

88
00:06:42,835 --> 00:06:46,260
They have a better conditions, resources, and other things over there.

89
00:06:46,260 --> 00:06:47,639
Wait, what do you mean, Gao Bin?

90
00:06:47,639 --> 00:06:51,320
Nothing. It's for your own good.

91
00:06:51,320 --> 00:06:54,357
Why don't I believe it? You're letting me go?

92
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:03,660
Every parent wishes the best for their children.

93
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:05,940
No matter how reluctant they feel,

94
00:07:05,940 --> 00:07:08,626
they shouldn't hinder their children's future.

95
00:07:09,620 --> 00:07:11,480
Your mom can provide a better life for you.

96
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:13,962
As your father, I'm happy for you.

97
00:07:16,140 --> 00:07:17,686
You...

98
00:07:19,339 --> 00:07:21,439
You don't need to worry about anything.

99
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:23,725
We will take care of ourselves.

100
00:07:26,979 --> 00:07:29,020
I won't say much else.

101
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:33,177
I wish you a pleasant journey.

102
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:07,285
Dad, play a song.

103
00:08:11,620 --> 00:08:13,390
Thank you.

104
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:15,537
What's there to thank me for?

105
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:20,352
Focus on your studies when you get there.

106
00:08:24,289 --> 00:08:30,922
♫ The white city , the gray wallpaper ♫

107
00:08:30,922 --> 00:08:38,782
♫ The night sky after shooting stars have left ♫

108
00:08:38,782 --> 00:08:45,522
♫ The warm shadows fading in the night ♫

109
00:08:45,522 --> 00:08:53,442
♫ We laugh and ramble about so many interesting things in our future ♫

110
00:08:53,442 --> 00:08:59,620
♫ The wasted times we went through together ♫

111
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:04,759
What are you doing? Let's go.

112
00:09:06,980 --> 00:09:09,480
Can you not get a divorce?

113
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:11,148
No.

114
00:09:14,579 --> 00:09:16,600
- Let's go.
- Gao Bin is such a coward.

115
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:18,539
What would he do if you leave?

116
00:09:18,539 --> 00:09:20,488
What are you saying?

117
00:09:21,380 --> 00:09:24,400
The train is about to leave. If you're not leaving, I'm leaving!

118
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:28,010
I don't have to take you with me.

119
00:09:28,010 --> 00:09:33,180
♫ There's no such name in reality ♫

120
00:09:35,299 --> 00:09:37,839
What's this? Are you threatening me?

121
00:09:37,839 --> 00:09:40,920
So what if I'm threatening you?

122
00:09:43,419 --> 00:09:45,179
I'll ask you one last time.

123
00:09:45,179 --> 00:09:47,214
Are you leaving or not?

124
00:09:49,819 --> 00:09:52,039
I'll count to three.

125
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:55,905
One, two,

126
00:09:55,905 --> 00:09:57,680
three!

127
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:59,979
I'm not leaving!

128
00:09:59,979 --> 00:10:02,420
You two stay together then!

129
00:10:03,460 --> 00:10:05,919
Mommy!

130
00:10:06,620 --> 00:10:08,779
Mom!

131
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:14,997
♫ I live at an address that never existed ♫

132
00:10:14,997 --> 00:10:23,385
♫ Like the beginning of when space-time suddenly intersects ♫

133
00:10:23,385 --> 00:10:31,677
♫ Confused of the unknown, confused for a moment, confused for a lifetime ♫
♫ My memories are full of ripples as if the wind blew here ♫

134
00:10:31,677 --> 00:10:35,614
It's okay. We'll live together.

135
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:38,002
You won't lose out on anything.

136
00:10:38,002 --> 00:10:44,127
♫ It is a house I have never visited ♫

137
00:10:44,127 --> 00:10:52,410
♫ Yet it left me with a lot of luxuries ♫

138
00:10:52,410 --> 00:10:58,835
♫ All attachments are just momentary ♫

139
00:10:58,835 --> 00:11:07,960
♫ How appropriate the ending is, just like how I presumed it would be ♫

140
00:11:18,319 --> 00:11:20,579
Why are you sitting here?

141
00:11:20,579 --> 00:11:26,359
Gao Yang is going to Beijing tomorrow. If you don't go see him, you won't have a chance later.

142
00:11:26,359 --> 00:11:28,020
I'm not going.

143
00:11:28,020 --> 00:11:30,539
Why not? Aren't you best friends?

144
00:11:30,539 --> 00:11:34,699
We made a deal when we were younger to stay in Tieyuan together forever!

145
00:11:34,699 --> 00:11:38,459
He's leaving all of sudden. What kind of man is he?

146
00:11:38,459 --> 00:11:42,799
I even left him a letter. He didn't have any reaction after reading it!

147
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:45,179
He doesn't even think of me as a friend!

148
00:11:45,179 --> 00:11:48,179
How would the things you both said as a child still count?

149
00:11:48,179 --> 00:11:51,280
All right, don't be mad. Quickly go now.

150
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:54,360
- I'm not going!
- Look at you.

151
00:11:54,360 --> 00:11:56,599
Fine. Don't go then.

152
00:12:00,319 --> 00:12:03,659
Jin Beibei, Gao Yang told you to go downstairs.

153
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:07,659
Then I'm going to tell him you're not coming.

154
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,730
Wait!

155
00:12:12,459 --> 00:12:14,860
Tell him to wait for me downstairs.

156
00:12:14,860 --> 00:12:17,220
Beibei, what's wrong with you? Did you see a ghost?

157
00:12:17,220 --> 00:12:19,419
I saw you.

158
00:12:21,140 --> 00:12:23,460
- Why is everyone here?
- They are all here to say goodbye to me.

159
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:28,320
Come on, hold up the confetti. On my command. Hurry, hurry.

160
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:31,380
Come on. One, two...

161
00:12:33,699 --> 00:12:35,839
I'm free!

162
00:12:35,839 --> 00:12:40,626
Gao Yang, what? Are you happy to leave us?

163
00:12:41,620 --> 00:12:45,899
I don't want our farewell to be too sad. There's no use crying about it, right?

164
00:12:45,899 --> 00:12:48,919
Come on. We are best friends.

165
00:12:48,919 --> 00:12:53,579
I'll only be gone for a few days. Don't let it affect our relationship. Here, take it!

166
00:12:53,579 --> 00:12:55,145
Beibei.

167
00:12:55,145 --> 00:12:58,479
Let's eat ice cream. Let's have fun today!

168
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:00,319
How would we have fun?

169
00:13:00,319 --> 00:13:04,920
In a while, we'll go karaoke, then play billiards, and finally, eat some stew in iron pots.

170
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:06,539
I'll pay for everything.

171
00:13:06,539 --> 00:13:10,100
Just one meal? You still owe Mi Jia 20 meals!

172
00:13:10,100 --> 00:13:13,659
And Xiaowen's game console, too! How can you break your promises?

173
00:13:13,659 --> 00:13:16,020
Beibei. That's too hard to do.

174
00:13:16,020 --> 00:13:18,999
You're just a liar! You can't keep any of your promises!

175
00:13:18,999 --> 00:13:20,762
Beibei!

176
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:24,379
If she doesn't want to eat, we'll eat without her. Let's have fun.

177
00:13:24,379 --> 00:13:27,560
Gao Yang, hurry up and go comfort her.

178
00:13:28,799 --> 00:13:30,837
Then you guys have some ice cream first.

179
00:13:32,579 --> 00:13:36,099
Beibei. Beibei. Beibei.

180
00:13:36,099 --> 00:13:37,299
Beibei, what's wrong?

181
00:13:37,299 --> 00:13:39,100
Get out.

182
00:13:39,100 --> 00:13:43,140
Wait. Why are you throwing a tantrum? We're best friends.

183
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:45,299
Besides, if you have any problems,

184
00:13:45,299 --> 00:13:46,659
we can talk about it later.

185
00:13:46,659 --> 00:13:48,979
Our classmates will laugh at us.

186
00:13:48,979 --> 00:13:52,299
I have nothing to say to you.

187
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:07,220
Hello? Then you can talk to me through this.

188
00:14:07,220 --> 00:14:12,519
You're going to leave. Who am I supposed to talk to?

189
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:16,720
I... I am leaving. Well, you can talk to Xiaowen.

190
00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:20,240
I already made a deal with Xiaowen. He'll take care of you from now on.

191
00:14:20,980 --> 00:14:25,960
I already taught him your secret codes. If you need answers for an exam, you can ask him.

192
00:14:25,960 --> 00:14:28,648
His grades are even better than mine.

193
00:14:28,648 --> 00:14:32,699
Why did you ask him?

194
00:14:32,699 --> 00:14:39,200
He has Mi Jia. Why should he take care of me?

195
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:43,500
You should take care of them then. Xiaowen and Mi Jia are both orphans.

196
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:48,519
As my best friend, shouldn't you take care of them after I leave?

197
00:14:48,519 --> 00:14:51,000
But... But...

198
00:14:51,000 --> 00:14:53,620
- But...
- Don't do that. Beibei, don't be upset.

199
00:14:53,620 --> 00:14:56,839
They are all waiting for us. Let's go eat stew in iron pots.

200
00:14:56,839 --> 00:15:00,160
Then when you go to Beijing, you're not allowed to see Wang Cailing.

201
00:15:00,939 --> 00:15:03,359
Who's Wang Cailing?

202
00:15:05,439 --> 00:15:10,559
Sis, I saw Gao Yang add Wang Cailing's QQ number in the internet bar!

203
00:15:10,559 --> 00:15:12,480
Gao Yang!

204
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,819
- No, no. I didn't!
- Gao Yang!

205
00:15:13,819 --> 00:15:17,080
She didn't accept it yet! She didn't accept it yet! You little brat!

206
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:20,980
Jin Doudou, when did you go to an internet bar?

207
00:15:21,000 --> 00:15:23,480
Stop right there! Stop right there!

208
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:26,380
Jin Doudou, stop right there!

209
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:29,120
- Jin Doudou, stop right there!
- What's going on?

210
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:31,579
- Catch him! Stop sweeping! Help me catch him!
- Stay right there!

211
00:15:31,579 --> 00:15:33,999
- Where are you running off to? What happened?
- Stop running!

212
00:15:33,999 --> 00:15:38,080
Stop running! Don't step on it!

213
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,880
Having fun now, are you?

214
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:43,939
Little brat, don't you run again!

215
00:17:32,900 --> 00:17:36,339
You don't want them anymore? I'll send them to the orphanage then.

216
00:17:36,339 --> 00:17:37,992
Go ahead.

217
00:17:39,720 --> 00:17:43,360
- I'll thank you on behalf of them.
- It's nothing.

218
00:17:43,360 --> 00:17:46,600
By the way, give me the address of the orphanage.

219
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:49,179
I'll send them something during the holidays and festivals.

220
00:17:49,179 --> 00:17:51,620
Have fun in Beijing.

221
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:55,259
- Did you pack everything?
- Yes, I did.

222
00:17:55,259 --> 00:17:59,619
- You only have one bag?
- My mom said she'll buy me everything when I'm in Beijing.

223
00:18:01,159 --> 00:18:02,737
Let's go.

224
00:18:04,559 --> 00:18:06,594
Brother Bin, I'm leaving now.

225
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:12,432
This rascal is handsome! You are like me back then. Not bad.

226
00:18:12,432 --> 00:18:18,260
Look at you. How old are you now? Your collar is still so sloppy.

227
00:18:19,879 --> 00:18:22,900
Take good care of yourself when you get to Beijing.

228
00:18:22,900 --> 00:18:24,380
Don't worry. My mom will be there.

229
00:18:24,380 --> 00:18:28,119
Your mom is not reliable. She's too busy to take care of you.

230
00:18:28,119 --> 00:18:30,459
I won't fight with you today.

231
00:18:31,690 --> 00:18:33,939
- Mr. Gao, your phone.
- I won't answer it. Let's go.

232
00:18:33,939 --> 00:18:35,979
Answer it. It won't take too long.

233
00:18:35,979 --> 00:18:38,128
I'll go answer it.

234
00:18:39,930 --> 00:18:44,159
Gao Yang, I'm telling you, you can't just play once you get to Beijing.

235
00:18:44,159 --> 00:18:45,900
Mr. Gao.

236
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:48,359
Who is it? Tell him I'm busy.

237
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:51,011
His mom.

238
00:18:52,019 --> 00:18:53,220
Go on. Quickly go.

239
00:18:53,220 --> 00:18:55,384
- Hurry up.
- Okay.

240
00:18:59,780 --> 00:19:02,000
Xiao Hong.

241
00:19:03,339 --> 00:19:05,580
- Hello?
- Gao Bin, I can't pick up Gao Yang today.

242
00:19:05,580 --> 00:19:07,399
You're not coming?

243
00:19:09,459 --> 00:19:11,540
Wait, what do you mean, Anna?

244
00:19:11,540 --> 00:19:13,979
- Who called? Hurry up.
- Okay!

245
00:19:13,979 --> 00:19:16,040
The school called.

246
00:19:16,900 --> 00:19:21,940
There are some last-minute changes. Gao Yang can't come to Beijing anymore. Let him stay in Tieyuan.

247
00:19:21,940 --> 00:19:24,199
Stop dawdling. Hurry up!

248
00:19:24,199 --> 00:19:25,929
Right away.

249
00:19:28,319 --> 00:19:30,939
What do you mean, Anna?

250
00:19:30,939 --> 00:19:36,339
We've come this far and now you're telling me you're not letting Gao Yang go to Beijing for schooling anymore. Are you playing with us?

251
00:19:36,339 --> 00:19:40,619
I have my reasons. You should comfort Gao Yang. I still have things to do. I'm hanging up.

252
00:19:40,619 --> 00:19:46,180
Gao Bin is so unreliable. He surely won't be able to take good care of you. I feel so bad.

253
00:19:46,180 --> 00:19:47,867
Anna...

254
00:20:00,170 --> 00:20:03,140
Are we leaving or not? If you're not leaving, then I'll leave on my own.

255
00:20:03,140 --> 00:20:04,754
Coming.

256
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:18,980
You're done talking?

257
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:23,130
- So slow. Let's hurry up and leave.
- No, no. Wait a minute.

258
00:20:23,130 --> 00:20:25,599
- What is it?
- Well,

259
00:20:26,979 --> 00:20:28,600
let's have a chat before you go.

260
00:20:28,600 --> 00:20:32,760
- Chat about what? I...
- Let's chat for a while.

261
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:36,600
- Put your bag down. Put it down. It's really heavy.
- Quickly speak.

262
00:20:41,060 --> 00:20:42,934
Well...

263
00:20:44,659 --> 00:20:46,496
That...

264
00:20:51,760 --> 00:20:53,667
I...

265
00:20:54,500 --> 00:20:56,780
Here's what I'm thinking.

266
00:20:58,140 --> 00:20:59,659
Let's continue with the topic from last time.

267
00:20:59,659 --> 00:21:01,400
For your physical and psychological health, and your future,

268
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:04,659
I've decided that you shouldn't go to school in Beijing. It's settled then!

269
00:21:04,659 --> 00:21:08,840
Wait, why are you doing that again? Stop joking around. My mom will be here soon.

270
00:21:08,840 --> 00:21:12,859
No, no. No, that's not it. Gao Yang.

271
00:21:12,859 --> 00:21:17,360
Maybe you should... listen to Xiaowen's opinion.

272
00:21:17,360 --> 00:21:20,079
Maybe... you shouldn't go to Beijing.

273
00:21:20,079 --> 00:21:21,938
See? You see?

274
00:21:24,060 --> 00:21:26,199
Right?

275
00:21:26,199 --> 00:21:28,041
Who called you?

276
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:32,095
The school.

277
00:21:35,979 --> 00:21:37,727
The school.

278
00:21:49,100 --> 00:21:51,219
Was it my mom who called?

279
00:22:01,739 --> 00:22:04,300
Was it my mom who called?

280
00:22:04,300 --> 00:22:06,219
She doesn't want me to go to Beijing anymore?

281
00:22:06,219 --> 00:22:08,111
How is that possible?

282
00:22:10,179 --> 00:22:12,559
I'm the one who doesn't want you to go.

283
00:22:12,559 --> 00:22:14,683
It's as simple as that.

284
00:22:18,140 --> 00:22:22,440
My mom changed her mind again? I'll ask her myself.

285
00:22:22,440 --> 00:22:23,998
Gao Yang.

286
00:22:29,280 --> 00:22:31,620
It has nothing to do with your mom.

287
00:22:31,620 --> 00:22:33,786
It's me.

288
00:22:33,786 --> 00:22:36,100
I'm reluctant to let you go.

289
00:22:39,870 --> 00:22:42,240
Then I'll wait for her.

290
00:22:44,060 --> 00:22:46,757
Gao Yang! Gao Yang!

291
00:22:48,919 --> 00:22:51,500
Gao Yang, the call was from Auntie! She said—

292
00:22:51,500 --> 00:22:56,019
She said she'd come to pick me up so she has to come! If she doesn't come today, I'll wait until she does.

293
00:22:56,839 --> 00:22:59,420
Gao Yang! Gao Yang!

294
00:23:25,419 --> 00:23:27,442
Don't stop me!

295
00:23:27,442 --> 00:23:28,920
I won't stop you.

296
00:23:29,540 --> 00:23:31,283
I'll wait with you.

297
00:23:41,590 --> 00:23:43,900
- Hello, Mr. Gao.
- Hello, Mr. Gao.

298
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:51,019
- Hello, Mr. Gao.
- Hello.

299
00:24:50,659 --> 00:24:52,300
Mr. Gao.

300
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:54,520
- You're off work?
- Yes, I'm off work.

301
00:24:54,520 --> 00:24:57,416
- Mr. Gao.
- Hello.

302
00:25:11,060 --> 00:25:12,380
- Bin.
- Hello.

303
00:25:12,380 --> 00:25:14,340
You all... Who are you waiting for here?

304
00:25:14,340 --> 00:25:15,980
- My mom.
- That's right.

305
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:18,060
It's been a whole day and you still haven't seen her?

306
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:20,108
She'll come soon.

307
00:25:20,108 --> 00:25:21,380
Alright, then.

308
00:25:21,380 --> 00:25:22,380
See you later.

309
00:25:22,380 --> 00:25:23,835
Okay.

310
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:04,719
Yangyang, are you hungry? Let's go get something to eat.

311
00:26:04,719 --> 00:26:08,319
I don't want to eat. I'll eat when I get to Beijing.

312
00:26:10,179 --> 00:26:12,459
When I get to Beijing,

313
00:26:12,459 --> 00:26:15,020
I'll go and eat roast duck first.

314
00:26:15,020 --> 00:26:17,144
After that, we'll eat boiled sliced mutton.

315
00:26:17,780 --> 00:26:21,840
My mom said there's a new hamburger place.

316
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:25,479
The... The fries there are so thick.

317
00:26:26,499 --> 00:26:28,939
I'll eat it for three days in a row.

318
00:26:30,140 --> 00:26:32,780
I'll then go watch the flag-raising ceremony.

319
00:26:32,780 --> 00:26:35,219
I'll go to concerts.

320
00:26:35,219 --> 00:26:41,039
I'll be a volunteer for the 2008 Beijing Olympic Games.

321
00:26:41,039 --> 00:26:43,760
I won't even have to pay to watch the events.

322
00:26:51,739 --> 00:26:54,040
Beijing roast duck is delicious.

323
00:26:55,380 --> 00:27:00,017
But our Tieyuan has a nice dumpling restaurant, too.

324
00:27:03,490 --> 00:27:08,240
Mr. Gao, does the dumpling restaurant have those with shrimp filling?

325
00:27:08,240 --> 00:27:09,340
Yes, it does!

326
00:27:09,340 --> 00:27:12,960
The shrimps are really big, even bigger than the dumplings.

327
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:15,939
What do they have besides dumplings?

328
00:27:15,939 --> 00:27:18,261
There is pork knuckle.

329
00:27:18,261 --> 00:27:22,539
The aroma of the pork knuckle in that restaurant...

330
00:27:22,539 --> 00:27:25,720
When you put it in your mouth, the juice just squirts out!

331
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:29,660
Take a bite of dumplings and a bite of pork knuckle, it's heavenly!

332
00:27:29,660 --> 00:27:34,279
Then... Then do they have dumplings with chives and eggs?

333
00:28:02,519 --> 00:28:04,820
Eat slowly.

334
00:29:08,799 --> 00:29:11,219
Sis, don't be sad.

335
00:29:24,860 --> 00:29:27,200
What is this, Jin Doudou?

336
00:29:27,919 --> 00:29:28,979
Is it sour?

337
00:29:28,979 --> 00:29:30,699
What do you think?

338
00:29:30,699 --> 00:29:32,019
Sour is right.

339
00:29:32,019 --> 00:29:35,180
That is what you're feeling right now.

340
00:29:35,180 --> 00:29:39,179
Jin Doudou, just you wait! Jin Doudou, stop right there!

341
00:29:39,179 --> 00:29:40,620
Do you believe I'll toss you off the roof right now?

342
00:29:40,620 --> 00:29:43,859
- Gao Yang, Gao Yang!
- Where?

343
00:29:47,219 --> 00:29:48,380
You're lying to me again!

344
00:29:48,380 --> 00:29:51,819
- It truly is Gao Yang!
- Gao Yang went to Beijing.

345
00:29:51,819 --> 00:29:55,650
My mood is like this weather now.

346
00:29:55,650 --> 00:29:57,690
Damp.

347
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:17,576
You're not going to sleep yet?

348
00:30:22,780 --> 00:30:24,845
I'm going to sleep, then.

349
00:30:29,699 --> 00:30:33,659
Why don't you take the bottom bunk tonight? I'll take the top bunk.

350
00:30:50,499 --> 00:30:52,147
Let's talk.

351
00:31:19,659 --> 00:31:21,616
Are you still upset?

352
00:31:24,340 --> 00:31:25,971
No.

353
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:30,465
Are you still blaming Auntie for not coming to pick you up?

354
00:31:31,499 --> 00:31:33,495
No, I'm not.

355
00:31:34,860 --> 00:31:37,640
She will surely come to pick you up.

356
00:31:38,459 --> 00:31:40,191
No way.

357
00:31:41,659 --> 00:31:43,760
She's just a liar.

358
00:31:45,780 --> 00:31:48,386
It's not the first time she lied to me.

359
00:31:49,380 --> 00:31:51,511
It's at least the 7th or 8th time already.

360
00:31:54,179 --> 00:31:56,999
In the past,

361
00:31:56,999 --> 00:32:00,599
she didn't come home because she needs to work and earn money.

362
00:32:01,739 --> 00:32:05,040
Now that she has money, she's still not coming back.

363
00:32:07,060 --> 00:32:09,150
She just doesn't care about me.

364
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:16,060
How can there be a mother who doesn't care about her child?

365
00:32:16,659 --> 00:32:19,159
At least you still have a mother.

366
00:32:21,259 --> 00:32:23,480
It's all the same to me whether I have one or not.

367
00:32:28,820 --> 00:32:31,060
She only cares about herself.

368
00:32:32,780 --> 00:32:37,389
She didn't want me when I was little. She still doesn't want me now.

369
00:32:50,780 --> 00:32:52,620
I don't miss her at all.

370
00:32:53,820 --> 00:32:57,619
I didn't miss her before. I don't miss her now.

371
00:32:57,619 --> 00:32:59,765
And I won't miss her in the future.

372
00:34:03,930 --> 00:34:09,040
Xiaowen, why is Gao Yang sitting on the abandoned railroad track?

373
00:34:09,040 --> 00:34:10,979
You keep running.

374
00:34:37,059 --> 00:34:38,901
Let's go home.

375
00:34:42,660 --> 00:34:44,220
I'll make you some good food.

376
00:34:44,220 --> 00:34:46,001
I don't want to eat.

377
00:34:50,900 --> 00:34:53,300
Are you still thinking about going to Beijing?

378
00:34:53,300 --> 00:34:54,860
No.

379
00:34:56,319 --> 00:35:00,160
Mr. Gao said your mom wanted to call and explain it to you.

380
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:01,743
I don't want to hear it.

381
00:35:02,610 --> 00:35:05,030
I know you're in a bad mood,

382
00:35:05,030 --> 00:35:08,130
but that won't solve any problems, Gao Yang.

383
00:35:11,600 --> 00:35:15,119
Don't entrust your life to your parents.

384
00:35:15,640 --> 00:35:20,000
If I think about the death of my parents all the time,

385
00:35:20,879 --> 00:35:22,922
how should I go on?

386
00:35:26,419 --> 00:35:29,339
No matter how they treat you,

387
00:35:29,339 --> 00:35:32,179
just do what you're supposed to do.

388
00:35:59,499 --> 00:36:02,639
I'm going to Beijing!

389
00:36:03,740 --> 00:36:05,820
You still want to run away?

390
00:36:06,740 --> 00:36:11,560
I'm not running away. This time, I will go openly and proudly.

391
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:16,920
I want to let my mom know that I will surely achieve my goals,

392
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,798
and make her regret it.

393
00:36:20,910 --> 00:36:24,520
You mentioned eating just now, right? Let's go and eat.

394
00:36:44,880 --> 00:36:46,651
Let's eat. Come on.

395
00:36:58,579 --> 00:37:00,700
Gao Yang, hurry up. You're going to be late!

396
00:37:00,700 --> 00:37:02,920
What is he doing?

397
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:06,259
- Mr. Gao, he already...
- I know.

398
00:37:06,259 --> 00:37:10,899
He still wants to go to Beijing, right? It's alright. He'll get over it in a few days.

399
00:37:10,899 --> 00:37:14,119
He's already been in there for 47 minutes.

400
00:37:18,740 --> 00:37:22,260
Gao Yang! Gao Yang, what are you doing?

401
00:37:22,979 --> 00:37:26,152
Stop dilly-dallying! You're going to be late, Gao Yang!

402
00:37:29,579 --> 00:37:32,579
Gao Yang, are you still in there?

403
00:37:32,579 --> 00:37:36,980
Don't try to jump out the window! There's a trash can down there!

404
00:37:37,719 --> 00:37:41,559
It's useless even if you go to the train station! I have eyes everywhere! Gao Yang!

405
00:37:41,559 --> 00:37:43,213
Gao...

406
00:38:15,140 --> 00:38:21,280
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

407
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:28,577
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

408
00:38:28,577 --> 00:38:34,535
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

409
00:38:34,535 --> 00:38:40,575
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

410
00:38:40,575 --> 00:38:47,300
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

411
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:52,867
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

412
00:38:52,867 --> 00:38:56,854
♫  To chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

413
00:38:56,854 --> 00:39:00,202
♫  Let's set sail on your dreams  ♫

414
00:39:00,202 --> 00:39:03,597
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

415
00:39:03,597 --> 00:39:10,257
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

416
00:39:10,257 --> 00:39:13,568
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

417
00:39:13,568 --> 00:39:17,680
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

418
00:39:17,680 --> 00:39:21,500
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

419
00:39:21,500 --> 00:39:29,460
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
